/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4178dc1ef46c85eeb895550890112a6bed36169b","tid":1057740,"uid":9777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:24:51.000Z","msg":"印度佬貪小便宜呢樣嘢真係無論咩階層都深入骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n犧牲所有嘢都係為咗平少少然後得不償失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 工作成日同印度佬交手，成千蚊嘢連10蚊5蚊差都要嗌一輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}